text: DONALD MACRAE, Crofter and Tailor, Cuaig (63)—examined.
—I came to see what was going on.
29938. Have you got any representation to make ?
—I don't know that we have anything to say which our own proprietor would not do for us.
29939. Is there anything you wish to do for yourselves?
—I think he himself will do all that we want,
